Package: CausalityExplained
Title: Explaining diseases causality using an extensive panel of traits
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Martin", "Tournaire", email = "martin.tournaire@u-paris.fr",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Causality Explained takes as input a set of predictor and an outcome. It outputs how much causality of the outcome the predictors explain.
